1. Tioh8 Chai Jin5-lui7 Kek8-ki5 Pai7-hoai7
Na7 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 hou7 lan2 khoaN3-beng5 jin5-lui7 e5 pun2-seng3 kek8-ki5 pai7-hoai7, lan2 thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok chiu7 choe3 boe7 ku2-tng5. Lan2 tioh8 chai, jin5-lui7 i2-keng pho3-san2 lah. Lan2 tioh8 beng5-pek8, jin5-lui7 long2 si2 ti7 in e5 ke3-sit kap choe7-koa3, in-ui7 ti7 lan2 jiok8-the2 e5 lai7-bin7 bo5 ho2 ti7-teh. Lan2 tioh8 jim7-bat lang5 e5 sim i2-keng phaiN2 kau3 kek8-thau5.
